com.bsandersen.CabConverter
Class CabFileNode

java.lang.Object
  com.bsandersen.CabConverter.CabFileNode

public class CabFileNode
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains the details for a given field of a QSO record or a heading line within a Cabrillo file. It can be a hard-coded text element like "QSO:" or "START-OF-LOG: 3.0" by having the field element type be "Text" and the value assigned to the string constant. It can also be a variable from the ADIF record or the UI elements of the PersonalData or the ContestDetails by mentioning the field name in the elementType (such as "Mode").

Author:
B. Scott Andersen (NE1RD)
